[SPEAKER_01] The strange thing, there was nothing wrong with my life.

59
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I had a nice life.

60
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] And I was absolutely miserable.

61
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] And I remember that my parents had gone out to do some shopping for Sunday, for Easter.

62
